      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么意思？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "开玩笑嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得我在开玩笑的时候，我就是在开玩笑",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要是觉得我说真的，也就成了真的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "【不懂，大人的世界好复杂】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我突然在想？其实你如何认为自己本质上是你如何认为他人眼中的你自己",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "干吗要上哲学课？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "你一天到晚上课不累吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "还真不累",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就早上两节课",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "【轻松愉快】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "好了，我不是故意抬杠，在惹你生气",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我觉得你好像挺在意他人的看法的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚好是说这句话的时机，我就说了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "看你这话说的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "有人不在意他人的看法吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "谁不是活在他人的评价体系中呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "别说你还真别说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "我曾经和一个心理医生聊过天，我问他谁的人格是完全健全的呢？在当今社会谁不会觉得自己的性格有些缺憾呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "心理医生说我啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我和我的很多同事们，我们都认为自己的人格很健全，也经得起评估",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我当时就有点无语了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "【擦汗】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "。你怎么会和心理医生聊天？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "你也有抑郁症？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没有啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们搞教育的总是要懂点心理学的，所以有时候会向他们取取经",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你有抑郁症吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "这从何说起呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "我什么都没说，我看起来像有病吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "你用了也字",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得一般只有自己得抑郁症才会对别人的这么敏感?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我说我要是得了抑郁症，你会不会觉得很矫情？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "生病就是生病啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "难道有人会说发烧了是因为矫情才会抱怨吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "可有人会说，经常发烧的人是体质差，不爱锻炼，生活习惯不好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "好就像是有人得了抑郁症，也会被说是因为闲得慌，心理素质太脆弱。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道我听到那个心理医生这么堂而皇之的说出那种话之后，为什么会无语吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "？为什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得在挨饿的人面前，能够吃饱的人咀嚼的声音小点，也是一种善良",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然我没有抑郁症，但是他作为一个专业的心理医生，会接触到很多抑郁症患者",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "抑郁症患者肯定不希望自己很痛苦的时候去找心理医生咨询类似的问题时，得到这样的回答",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "姓林医生跟我处在较为平等的状态下，都能摆出这么一副高高的姿态，我有理由相信",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "他对受访者的姿态可能更傲慢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "是的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "这和我刚才被评价的矫不矫情有什么关系？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得评价抑郁症是吃饱了，闲着没事干的那一部分人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是因为他们太吃饱了。他们故意在挨饿的人面前咀嚼的很大声",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们没有基本的共情心理，甚至可以说是不善良",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "？我一开始觉得自己得了抑郁症的时候，一直要去找医生看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道我自己的状态已经不对劲了，也整天很低落，吃不下也睡不好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我身边朋友都跟我说啊，你有抑郁情绪是很正常的，抑郁情绪并不是等于有抑郁症",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们让我快点找个医生看看，说我确诊了没有抑郁症之后，就不会东想西想了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我就去找了心理医生，确诊真的得了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "【无话可说】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我就把诊疗结果告诉朋友们了，我不知道我当时带着一种什么样的心理跟他们说的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我就是觉得不舒服，很不舒服",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "是因为你的痛苦被漠视，被否定了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你要向他们证，你不是在无病呻吟",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "可能吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也说不清楚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "没关系",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "人也不是什么问题都要得到答案",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你现在有在吃药吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "以前吃，现在只吃点斯诺斯或者艾斯左伦维持睡眠",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "你失眠很严重吗？要吃艾司唑仑",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "据我所知，只有比较严重的情况，医生才会开这个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我有植物神经调节障碍",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "这是什么病？我第一次听说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不算什么病吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是对时间失去感觉了，晚上睡不着，白天睡不醒这样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "算是比较严重的生物钟失衡吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "【恭喜你，都学会抢答了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "睡不着确实很难受，怪不得你暴躁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过没有吃其他药，是你除了睡眠之外的状况都比较良好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "还行吧，过得去，没有到糟糕的程度",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实大多数人都抑郁症也就是在一个还好的水平，不会让人真想死，但活着也挺累的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "对，有点空虚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "hh那我不得不说电影，电视剧真是伟大的发明",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "还记得我们刚才在聊什么吗？你向我要电影推荐",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "看点电影吧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我推荐三傻大闹宝莱坞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "温暖搞笑又治愈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "看过了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "这么经典电影早就看了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师，你把我当文盲了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "绝对没有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "就冲你这两天跟我说的话，说出的思想，你绝对不是文盲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "是因为我自己很喜欢这部电影，经常重温，所以逢人就安利",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "看罗拉快跑？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "女主是不是红色的短发一直在跑？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "你看过？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我刷到过电影切片",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "女主蛮飒的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，这部电影值得一看的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "只看电影切片有点可惜了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "女主一直在跑，一直在跑，在非常简单的情景下做出了很有趣的故事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我有空看看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我以为你向我要了安利，是马上就会去看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "大哥，我们是朝九晚五打工人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们工作日下了班之后是要躺在床上无脑的刷一会短视频的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "那么本朝九晚五，打工人现在要去填表格了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么表格？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "一些不重要的教学项目评估表格",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "我去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "拜拜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
